Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,来自异次元的侵入者MU\N将东京与世隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,17岁少年神名绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,在突然受到神秘战斗机攻击而发生混乱的东京…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,与奇异的少女 美屿玲香相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,两人好不容易来到东京湾的地下神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,在那里，他们看到了一只漂浮的巨卵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,从那颗卵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,像是受到了玲香歌声的引导，从卵中诞生出的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,神秘的巨神——RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,绫人登上RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,击败了巨型兵器——Dolem
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,但是，在战斗中绫人失去了玲香…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,他又发现养育自己的母亲流着蓝色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,精神上受到了冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,乘着RahXephon逃出东京的绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,第一次了解到世界的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,东京竟然是被人类的敌人——MU所统治着的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,引导绫人的是来自对抗MU的组织…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,TERRA的情报员 紫东遥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,绫人现在必须操纵RahXephon去对抗\N他过去一直居住的那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0150,,那个他的朋友、邻居和母亲居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉丽亚·立特巴克号现在\N开始进入根来彼方港
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰抵达港口的时间预计是12：37
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概会与我们同时到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样正好，接受货物之后我们\N就可以立即起航了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那岛上停留多久也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也是个外来者，怎么不接受健康检查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和动物不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把猫带上舰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违反了华盛顿条约吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰既将进入根来彼方港
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在离舰的时候你要负责把猫带走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名绫人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在进港之前，请把你的表调整到…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月树博士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已经在我面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很值得一看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个巨大的人偶作为5A级MU制品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将被编制到琉球MU技术基础研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望移交我舰的转移作业能立刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我听说你计划\N将O.P.A.R.T.S.用于军事目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:45.26,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}O.P.A.R.T.S.：Out of Place Artifacts的缩写，考古学名词\N某个地层中出土的不属于该地层地质年代的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为这个Overlord作战\N我们也付出了很大代价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:49.93,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Overlord作战：盟军诺曼底登陆的作战代号\NTERRA入侵Tokyo Jupiter的行动也以此命名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用介意我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TERRA是地球联合的下属组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:03:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收5A级O.P.A.R.T.S.时\N和我军情报员一起回来的那个男孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么处置？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一个小孩还有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经有足够多的Tokyo Jupiter人类样本了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布奇，布奇！你去哪儿了？喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎，遥小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令谈到关于手表的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说我们所在的城市\N和外面的世界之间有一个时间差吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确两边的季节也不一样，我有些惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，绫人君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的是这里的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面显示的是Tokyo Jupiter的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较一下表上数字变化的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是时差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，你可以先回房间去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些悄悄话要说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女人之间的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面时你请我喝的苦艾酒…\N成了我一个开销很大的嗜好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:23.44,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}苦艾酒：用苦艾和其它一些药草精制的有苦茴香或甘草味\N酒精浓度为70%左右的绿色洋酒，因为有毒性在很多国家被禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你是唯一的生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是艾尔菲·哈迪亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥·紫东，因为你是情报部的人，\N我才会当面问你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要回答：“yes”或“no”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咱们上次喝酒的时候我没拿收据，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次overlord作战的内情你清楚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同伴们的血是不是为\N那个无聊的男孩白流了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里听来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想知道你是否了解这次任务的内情！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来下周中国餐馆是去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这艘船里也有发廊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个招牌最初是战地医院的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些颜色象征着\N红色的血管（动脉）和蓝色的血管（静脉）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的血是红色的，但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有两种不同颜色的血管？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面不行，这儿，从后面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:06:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前扣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它扣在腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维生模块
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在发廊里的椅子上时，我想\N尽可能地放松所以总是把它脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我想把身上衣服都脱掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果全部脱掉后再剪头发的话\N就可能要挨骂了对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，olin！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎，等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要运走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么处理战利品和你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一色真，TERRA的合作者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么处理它？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把它送到联合的研究设施去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人偶的管理权和拥有权\N已经属于地球联合了，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸上怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点儿问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有麻烦的话找我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云君，真是个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像误会了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道还想强调你对于O.P.A.R.T.S.\N拥有任何形式的所有权吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，绫人君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我事先向你解释的话也许会好点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官，O.P.A.R.T.S.运转作业完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤利西斯号申请起航的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后呢？我是不是也应该被运走呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不会违反华盛顿条约…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷的成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好和他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该好好了解一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己现在的处境…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名绫人君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从深渊中浮出的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了少年的面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的眼睛，这种音色…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令是想让你快点熟悉外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也那样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你们这些外面的人很喜欢逼迫别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于像我这样的人，你们都带着\N一种“要教育教育他”的优越感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了这份报纸之后，就很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少写这些报纸的人是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本就不认为我们是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物理分析已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是MU PHASE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MU族吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能完全这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，先按MU族处理掉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，你认为我也是那样看待你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫东遥大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫东遥大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即到舰桥去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用会儿功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是没有司令的声音识别不能开启的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU族监禁室对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果强行打开的话，里面就会发生爆炸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与人类样本的分子对比分析已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试验所有的核苷酸序列，\N都有MU PHASE反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您，放他出来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会和我们合作的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，他和我们一样是流着红色血液的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不清楚自己的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况了解真实的线索就摆在他面前\N他却悠闲地在画画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么样的环境造就了他这种性格的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于那一类的东西，它刚刚打破瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡逻中的U-07的来电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触Yellow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标Yellow-1在Amber-48\N正从04向05匀速运动中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标在SOSUS（声响监视系统）上确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触RED
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认目标是D-1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全岛进入紧急警戒状态，DEFCON-3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会从莉丽亚·立特巴克号上下达命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全岛进入紧急警戒状态，发布DEFCON-3命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们终于出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发报给U-07
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据旗舰的判断，允许使用贫铀弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力阻止目标D-1前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-07，这里是莉丽亚·立特巴克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-07，请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-07正在紧急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1速度150，前进中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标已经突破第一警戒区域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1正侵入88区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启第二拦截系统，第四级
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根来彼方受到类似D-1不明物体的攻击，正在交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们提前出发是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色抽到了下下签
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出发？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战机的武器解除了，而且你没法从这里起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻像系统，出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种机动性是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会般声音再次从远处传来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，它们将被毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏力超出了我们的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是那样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度，170！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船坞大门保护性封闭，完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部雷达上没有发现D-1的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被动声纳没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被动和主动声纳都没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多普勒效应雷达的反应急速增加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标的相对坐标…零！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本舰正下方！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被关起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1现正直接攻击本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员进入紧急迎击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急迎击状态！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再呆在这里，我会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！有人听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥小姐！遥小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥！遥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！混蛋！混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连遥小姐也骗我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么他妈的“正确的时间”！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！O.P.A.R.T.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海岸上发现新的能源反应！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明物体高速接近中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直接向我方高速逼近中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是来找绫人君的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监禁室中的生命反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视摄像机不能确认神名绫人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道已经在RahXephon里面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们干的好事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是TERRA的责任！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你把命令状给那个大家伙看看如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来把他监禁起来并非上策
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然值得一看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎归来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封闭的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触摸着的回忆奏出平静的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon第五乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根来彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音